    "AI也有可能出错，输出仅供参考，请亲自核查重要信息。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "AI can make mistakes. Output is for reference only; verify important information yourself."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "AI也有可能出错，输出仅供参考，请亲自核查重要信息。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "AI 也有可能出錯，輸出僅供參考，請親自查證重要資訊。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "All cached tools" : {

    },
    "Anthropic Messages sends the API Key as x-api-key and automatically adds anthropic-version. The API Key is stored in Keychain." : {

    },
    "Anthropic Messages uses v1/messages as the default endpoint and x-api-key for authentication. Model names ending in [1m] are sent with 1M context while the suffix is removed from the actual model value. With Claude Code impersonation enabled, all models use Bearer authentication and automatically add beta=true, 1M context, Claude Code headers, and request body fields. Max Tokens only applies to the current configuration." : {

    },
    "API Key" : {

    },
    "API 类型" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "API Type"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "API 类型"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "API 類型"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "apiFormat.anthropicMessages.requestFooter" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Anthropic Messages uses v1/messages as the default endpoint and x-api-key for authentication. Model names ending in [1m] are sent with 1M context while the suffix is removed from the actual model value. With Claude Code impersonation enabled, all models use Bearer authentication and automatically add beta=true, 1M context, Claude Code headers, and request body fields. Max Tokens only applies to the current configuration."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Anthropic Messages 默认 endpoint 是 v1/messages，默认认证使用 x-api-key；模型名以 [1m] 结尾时会按 1M 上下文发送但实际 model 会去掉该后缀。开启 Claude Code 伪装后，所有模型都会改用 Bearer，并自动附加 beta=true、1M context、Claude Code headers 和请求体字段。Max Tokens 仅对当前配置生效。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Anthropic Messages 預設 endpoint 為 v1/messages，認證預設使用 x-api-key；模型名稱以 [1m] 結尾時，會以 1M 上下文傳送，實際 model 值則會移除該後綴。開啟 Claude Code 偽裝後，所有模型都會改用 Bearer，並自動附加 beta=true、1M context、Claude Code headers 和請求內容欄位。Max Tokens 僅對目前設定生效。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "apiFormat.openAIChatCompletions.requestFooter" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Chat Completions combines Endpoint with Base URL to form the final request URL. The default endpoint is chat/completions."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Chat Completions 会把 Endpoint 与 Base URL 拼成最终请求地址，默认 endpoint 是 chat/completions。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Chat Completions 會將 Endpoint 與 Base URL 組成最終請求位址，預設 endpoint 為 chat/completions。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "apiFormat.openAIResponses.requestFooter" : {
